---
title: American-Style BBQ Jackfruit with Garlic Rice, Pickled Onion & Slaw
description: Jackfruit marinated in saucy BBQ flavouring – our favourite (and totally irresistible) veggie alternative to pulled pork. Pair it with
our tried-and-true garlic rice method that's all yum and no fuss!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/american-style-bbq-jackfruit-e3ae7349.jpg
